Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.84,0:00:04.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,快!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.12,0:00:04.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,燒死她!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.23,0:00:07.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,燒了她我們就能得救
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.01,0:00:13.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,滾開!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.73,0:00:25.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,難道會跟那時一樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.94,0:00:31.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,迎來同樣的結局...!!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.44,0:00:36.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:41.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不想死的話 趕緊離開此地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.52,0:00:44.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我是很想逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.27,0:00:47.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.48,0:00:50.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,憑我一己之力辦不到什麼事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.32,0:00:53.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,或許我只是在意氣用事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.85,0:00:55.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但我一定要去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.75,0:00:57.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.02,0:01:00.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真的蒙您關照 死神先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.56,0:01:01.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼再見!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.35,0:01:07.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直像是去處理小事一般
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.86,0:01:09.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,匹夫之勇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.95,0:01:10.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,抑或是...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.36,0:01:17.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 這一切皆如蝕再臨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.37,0:01:19.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.87,0:01:23.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,憑人的力量無法更改這個祭典的情節
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.66,0:01:28.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,吾等已在因果循環當中
Comment: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:09.58,DefaultSub,,0,0,0,,/--------START---------/
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.58,0:03:10.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,很快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.20,0:03:12.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,還有片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.26,0:03:14.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我的生命就到頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.58,0:03:16.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那一刻才正是我存在的意義!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.33,0:03:18.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,至少在那最後一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.98,0:03:23.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,能從塔頂俯視我的世界消亡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.91,0:03:24.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,如果
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.04,0:03:27.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我也像那幾位負責拷問的人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.59,0:03:31.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在某地遇上那位僧侶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.88,0:03:35.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是也會迎來不同的一生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.56,0:03:41.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是也會成為他們當中的一員呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.16,0:03:44.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但我並沒有這種福分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.02,0:03:47.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 現在的我甚至覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.86,0:03:49.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,與其說我沒有福分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.99,0:03:53.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不如說在孤獨的塔頂俯視這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.41,0:03:56.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,才是我的存在意義
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.28,0:03:58.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,於我而言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.29,0:04:00.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這個一直仰望的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.54,0:04:02.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不過是個應該俯視的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.79,0:04:07.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,夠了 就讓它終結吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.13,0:04:13.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嬰兒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.22,0:04:16.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,三番四次救了那魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:21.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然他有著肉身 卻不是單純的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.23,0:04:24.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,已經快要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.23,0:04:29.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你也和我一樣嗎 異形嬰兒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.78,0:04:33.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一起上路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.62,0:04:43.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,至少我體內的新世界能成為你的搖籃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.16,0:04:45.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,做個好夢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.17,0:04:51.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那群愚民
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.24,0:04:55.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,做的事情跟邪教徒有什麼兩樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.22,0:04:59.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 這次可沒扔石頭那麼簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.03,0:05:03.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真想不到我們都還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.41,0:05:07.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 走快點 你這個邪教徒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.88,0:05:10.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了 看準時機就逃走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.49,0:05:15.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,您沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.52,0:05:18.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到會跟他們同行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:20.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然覺得我的事還沒暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.81,0:05:23.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但若不適當找個藉口離開的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:26.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 大叔 你來得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.29,0:05:30.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵 是怎麼回事呢 那個小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.71,0:05:32.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊? 我聽不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.42,0:05:34.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,別廢話 趕緊過來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.80,0:05:37.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,總之我先過去看看情況
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.41,0:05:38.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,失陪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.30,0:05:40.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個臭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.06,0:05:42.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.01,0:05:46.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,燒死她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.44,0:05:47.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,燒!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:48.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,快 燒死她!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.12,0:06:04.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,快 趕快!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:07.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,點起淨化的火焰!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.83,0:06:11.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,摩茲古斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.90,0:06:31.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,因果循環嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.73,0:06:33.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可似乎...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.61,0:06:35.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你認真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.36,0:06:37.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,最近我經常從這麼高的地方摔下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.03,0:06:40.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,也該習慣了!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.11,0:06:42.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這一切...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.79,0:06:48.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,並沒有...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.84,0:07:00.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就是現在 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.39,0:07:04.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...完全一致
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.64,0:07:10.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,休想!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:18.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,休想逃!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.58,0:07:27.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,出乎意料地 你並不是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.00,0:07:35.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...映在水面的倒影
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.84,0:07:39.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定是掀起水波的游魚亦未可知
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.63,0:07:43.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一個黑影將...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.78,0:07:44.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,摩茲古斯大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.90,0:07:56.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,摩茲古斯大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.23,0:07:57.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,天使大人...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.80,0:08:00.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,天使大人被打敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.11,0:08:03.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色惡魔打敗了天使大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.24,0:08:05.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.15,0:08:09.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...剛才瞬間掠過我眼前的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.29,0:08:11.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.75,0:08:18.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.55,0:08:25.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,次次都被你搶走我還用混?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.72,0:08:28.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,身為天使怎麼能揩小偷的油!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.51,0:08:29.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,又來一個!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.77,0:08:32.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,犯人是這個色狼 放過我!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.65,0:08:41.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.56,0:08:43.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,別過來別過來...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.33,0:08:50.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.79,0:08:53.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,還...還是動手了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.62,0:08:58.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這下再怎麼裝模作樣也殳辦法抵賴了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.25,0:09:01.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不畏懼神明的愚民
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.51,0:09:03.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,天罰馬上降臨!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.97,0:09:06.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,由我替天行道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.09,0:09:10.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,將你懲罰!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.22,0:09:13.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,看 摩茲古斯大人復活了!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.88,0:09:16.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他要為了我們跟惡魔對抗!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:19.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,摩茲古斯大人那副樣子...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.15,0:09:23.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,天使? 不 簡直是個怪...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.74,0:09:30.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你再怎麼揮舞強大的邪惡力量也是白費
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.91,0:09:32.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,請看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.45,0:09:37.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,聖書擊退了汙穢之刃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.33,0:09:40.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這正是吾信仰之源
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.38,0:09:43.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只要聖書在吾身上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.26,0:09:46.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,吾之肉身便不會受傷!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.51,0:09:50.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,聖書不是被貫穿了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.51,0:09:53.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,單純是那個怪物刀槍不入而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.10,0:09:57.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,雙胞胎 將魔女拿下!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.81,0:10:01.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,其餘之人皆處以鋸刑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.50,0:10:02.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.94,0:10:06.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你活著來到這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.44,0:10:11.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,說明我那四位弟子已被上天召回
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.66,0:10:19.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我要將你大卸八塊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:25.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,以此來餞別他們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.68,0:10:30.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他的力量跟使徒不相上下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.47,0:10:32.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但體格猶在使徒之上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.35,0:10:36.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,強力招來! 超力招來!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.52,0:10:40.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.35,0:10:45.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 別東張西望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.78,0:10:49.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,千手觀音轟擊!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.62,0:10:56.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,神之吐息!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.84,0:11:11.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,再也不想聽到你那無聊透頂的說教
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.55,0:11:13.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把你的嘴堵上!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.47,0:11:18.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,滋味如何!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.85,0:11:23.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,憑這三腳貓功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.98,0:11:28.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就想粉碎神賜予我的戰盔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.61,0:11:31.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,做夢!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.47,0:11:57.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,看樣子輪不到我們插手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.97,0:12:00.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,別說喪氣話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.52,0:12:01.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧了格斯大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.06,0:12:04.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我們才只需要對付兩個怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.02,0:12:08.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,操! 那是誰把我拖進這灘渾水的!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.40,0:12:10.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續留在這裏的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.65,0:12:13.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我會跟這些人一起被殺掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.24,0:12:19.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 艾倫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.13,0:12:29.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.97,0:12:32.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 不要! 啊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.14,0:12:40.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.06,0:12:41.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,她還活著 還有氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.89,0:12:45.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 別啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.71,0:12:48.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 那兩個傢伙飛來飛去的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:50.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一會兒也好 若能封住他們的活動的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.61,0:12:53.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話 就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.16,0:12:56.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我不幹了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.65,0:12:58.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 危急關頭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.32,0:13:00.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是精靈的力量也要藉助
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:01.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,危急關頭?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.20,0:13:02.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 對不起!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.60,0:13:04.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,看 他們來了 怎麼辦啊!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.83,0:13:06.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,看好了 猴崽子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.88,0:13:09.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,誰才是真正的天空霸主!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.59,0:13:12.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,巴克火花!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.43,0:13:16.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,還真是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.68,0:13:18.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...給你辦到了!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.35,0:13:25.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.66,0:13:34.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是前途可怕的小鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.57,0:13:36.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,雙胞胎...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.45,0:13:39.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你們好大的膽子!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.45,0:13:43.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.24,0:13:45.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你們對神就沒有一點畏懼之心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.71,0:13:49.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要阻止我執行神聖的任務嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.67,0:13:53.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此想拍神的馬屁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.96,0:13:57.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就將自己的項上人頭供奉給神如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.68,0:14:01.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不准你再動她一個手指頭!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.15,0:14:14.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,又過來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.65,0:14:18.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,摩茲古斯大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.06,0:14:19.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,請救救我們!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.26,0:14:20.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,神啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.57,0:14:21.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,天使大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.95,0:14:23.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,救命啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.58,0:14:32.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,千手觀音轟擊!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.75,0:14:34.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能全部躲開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.88,0:14:38.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我的攻擊跟他一比就是小巫見大巫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.13,0:14:39.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.86,0:14:54.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,跟被石頭砸了一般
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.53,0:14:58.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你聽不到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.82,0:15:00.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這些人的禱告!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.61,0:15:05.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,所有聚集此地的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.66,0:15:09.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,如今都齊心懇求得到救贖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.58,0:15:13.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你為了一個魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.00,0:15:20.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,便要犧牲成千上萬信徒的生命嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.26,0:15:23.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,別假仁假義了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.14,0:15:26.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,為何燒死大姐姐愚民便能得救
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.18,0:15:28.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,快!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.31,0:15:29.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,燒死魔女!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.35,0:15:32.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,別胡扯了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.90,0:15:37.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他們只是在...無力地祈禱而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.99,0:15:41.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,聚集了如此多人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.24,0:15:45.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在火燒眉毛之時
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.11,0:15:47.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他們這群廢物卻在求神拜佛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.91,0:15:52.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,成千上萬之人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:54.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要跟一個女人過不去!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.00,0:15:58.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,祈禱即是信仰!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.63,0:16:01.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,祈禱 然後將一切託付神明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.67,0:16:04.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那才是信仰的本質!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.68,0:16:07.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你這個不懂祈禱的傲慢之人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.47,0:16:09.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,給我悔過自身去!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.42,0:16:37.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,神之重壓!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.01,0:16:48.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,像你這種不信神之人絶不會有奇蹟降臨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.78,0:16:52.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在淨化的火焰中焚燒並好好反省吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.91,0:16:56.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,與其等待那偉大的奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.31,0:17:01.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡自己動手解決!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.53,0:17:04.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直抱著聖書
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.86,0:17:06.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,難道不是有舊傷?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.07,0:17:10.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,用自己最信任的事物守護著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.33,0:17:14.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,反過來說 那裏就是最脆弱的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.31,0:17:36.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,見了神跟他說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.65,0:17:38.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,少摻合我的事情!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:41.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,神啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.01,0:17:46.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在就去您身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.81,0:17:55.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但起碼要將這個神之敵一起帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.37,0:18:00.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,敬謝不敏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.38,0:18:03.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是最虔誠的你所要走的星光大道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:06.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,若我踏上去會遭報應的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.41,0:18:12.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你就獨自...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.02,0:18:17.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...升天吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.15,0:18:46.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.94,0:19:04.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,神啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:06.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.57,0:19:07.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.24,0:19:08.19,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,來人!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.19,0:19:09.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好暗!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.05,0:19:10.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好餓!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.14,0:19:12.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,畜生!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.58,0:19:17.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,太強了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.41,0:19:18.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,殺了她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.62,0:19:20.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,殺了那個女人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.41,0:19:21.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.62,0:19:23.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,別扯了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.84,0:19:24.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢才!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.48,0:19:25.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,快動手!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.27,0:19:39.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.52,0:19:43.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 痛 卡思嘉!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:01.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,塔!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.54,0:20:02.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,逃到塔裏面去!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.78,0:20:04.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,逃到高處!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.50,0:20:06.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,正面不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.51,0:20:07.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,繞到裏面去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.30,0:20:10.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,副團長 人群正湧入塔裏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.13,0:20:12.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有其他退路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.55,0:20:13.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.93,0:20:14.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,撤!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.09,0:20:17.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,全軍為民殿後!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.54,0:20:20.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 塔裏面也有怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.18,0:20:22.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,比留在這裏要好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.23,0:20:27.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,別怕 儘量保護更多的人進塔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.86,0:20:28.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,副團長!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.73,0:20:29.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,咋了?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.61,0:20:30.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.11,0:20:31.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等等!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.03,0:20:32.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,還有很多人...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.28,0:20:33.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,誰管你那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.57,0:20:35.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,快關門!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.01,0:20:36.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,關門關門!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.32,0:20:39.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 還有婦孺...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.11,0:20:40.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我進去!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.66,0:20:42.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.79,0:20:48.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這叫什麼事!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.59,0:20:49.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,又來坑我!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.69,0:20:51.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,副團長 該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.55,0:20:54.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,保護婦孺 組陣!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.59,0:21:00.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,最後一刻也不放棄希望才是真正的騎士!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.31,0:21:05.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了 現在正是展示我們騎士氣魄之時!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.12,0:21:06.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.31,0:21:10.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 照那個勢頭要爬上來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.82,0:21:13.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.78,0:21:14.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,火
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.78,0:21:16.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你們看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.37,0:21:23.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 那些汙穢怕火
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.96,0:21:26.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他死了比活著有用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.42,0:21:27.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,摩茲古斯大人...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.30,0:21:33.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不想死的就撿木頭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:35.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我怕火...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.96,0:21:36.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,誰管你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.18,0:21:38.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好咧!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.54,0:21:41.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你 與其在城穡上面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.93,0:21:44.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不如和我們一起進塔裏面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.01,0:21:46.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那簡直是羊入虎口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.14,0:21:49.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大部分怪物都會進塔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.15,0:21:51.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,對會攻破城門的敵人而言
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.61,0:21:53.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,固守城池毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.49,0:21:56.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,而且很快就天亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.78,0:22:00.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那些東西見了太陽便會消失或者力量滅弱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.76,0:22:03.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但光是照不到塔裏面去的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.87,0:22:06.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏的話最先被陽光照射到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.25,0:22:08.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,勝負關鍵在於能否到天亮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.33,0:22:11.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要活下去!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.30,0:22:22.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,劈開一條活路!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.35,0:22:25.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,劈開活路!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.26,0:21:13.57,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是該獨自跑路了呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:04:59.90,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,快點!
